# AI Integration Code Rules

## Provider Routing
All AI calls go through `ai-router.ts`. Route by task:
- Quality generation → Claude (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)
- Bulk generation → Mistral (mistral-large)
- Video/long docs → Gemini (gemini-2.0-flash)
- Web search → Perplexity (sonar-pro)
- Embeddings → OpenAI (text-embedding-3-small)

## Structured Output (MANDATORY)
Every LLM response MUST be validated via Instructor.js + Zod schema before DB write.
```typescript
const result = await instructor.chat.completions.create({
  model: "claude-sonnet-4-20250514",
  response_model: { schema: QuestionSchema, name: "Question" },
  messages: [{ role: "user", content: prompt }],
});
```

## Cost Control
- Check Redis cache before any AI call
- Log: provider, model, input_tokens, output_tokens, latency_ms, cost_usd
- Use Anthropic batch API for scraping jobs (50% discount)
- Gemini free tier first for video processing
